data.description: Beautiful split foyer home in Bent Tree neighborhood of Burke! Located on a spacious lot on a quiet street, this home features an open layout on the main level, including hardwood floors and a large eat-in kitchen. Three bedrooms and two bathrooms on main level, including primary bedroom with attached bath. Lower level includes two bedrooms, a full bathroom, laundry, and spacious rec room with fireplace. Deck off of dining area including an enclosed, screened area as well as an open air section. Two car garage. Conveniently located near commuter roads, great schools, and more!
